{"tid":909044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【米奇老鼠90歲】網上瘋傳米奇恐怖動畫　有人睇完自殺？","createTime":"2018-11-20T05:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T05:48:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27b1134bd7bbc7b472ed51af13d79ddc3b13502d","tid":909044,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"米奇老鼠日前迎來90歲生日，這個風摩全球大人細路的角色，為觀眾帶來無限歡樂。<br />\n但正所謂凡事都有兩面，在眾多米奇老鼠動畫中，原來出現過好一些引起爭議的劇情，其中最恐怖的要數一條長達9分鐘的短片，當中彌漫著絕望又陰森的氣氛，與大家心目中開心又健康的米奇，完全差天共地！<br />\n一條從未曝光的黑白米奇老鼠動畫《Suicide Mouse》，於2009年忽然在網上流傳，片長9分鐘其實沒劇情可言，只看到米奇老鼠頹廢地走在街道上，而背景的建築物不停重覆出現，配以奇怪又強烈的鋼琴聲，足以嚇人一跳。但更恐怖的是，中間突然出現黑畫，到6分鐘米奇再次出現時，背景鋼琴聲變成奇怪的人聲，而米奇的臉亦逐漸扭曲，露出齜牙裂嘴的樣子，令人心寒。<br />\n米奇越行越快，身後的建築物亦變得模糊，之後米奇連對眼都冇埋，背景音樂變成刺耳的奇怪尖叫人聲，米奇的臉更撕裂成兩半，最後畫面切換成米奇的大頭相，配以幾句俄文，翻譯成英文為「the sight of hell brings its viewers back in」（地獄的景象帶領觀眾回來）。<br />\n坊間有一說法是，當初是由迪士尼電影專家Leonard Maltin獲得這條短片，想將它收錄於米奇老鼠動畫DVD合集內，但他越看下去便越覺不妥，Leonard忍受不了，走出房間叫其他工作人員把短片看完，並將當中細節筆錄下來，豈料工作人員看畢影片後衝出房間，一臉蒼白用俄文連講7次：「Real suffering is not known」（未知的真正痛苦），之後搶去警衛的手槍自殺。<br />\n究竟這個故事是真是假，實在難以考究，相隔幾年又有另一個版本的《Suicide Mouse》出現在YouTube，片中米奇的下場更恐怖，是突然倒斃在街頭，身旁還有一支針筒，背景的尖叫聲更刺耳，有指這個版本是外國網民的山寨作，但在YouTube上的點撃率高達700萬，似乎大家對「暗黑米奇」甚有興趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2112513/org/474a47321349ef764aa208a3a7e4f5f0.jpg/i2zf9YuX5oWU9tdhMJHXHtmsueMuEk30fxS02H8UtNg?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2112513%2Forg%2F474a47321349ef764aa208a3a7e4f5f0.jpg%2Fi2zf9YuX5oWU9tdhMJHXHtmsueMuEk30fxS02H8UtNg%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=2b8b58bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2112516/org/b71a3f71444dbdc21cf69345cdd0eb1e.jpg/fZy3mZ1aCwL8EYbGBDNaCqKbMQhP7TdbfHnzq3x586s?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2112516%2Forg%2Fb71a3f71444dbdc21cf69345cdd0eb1e.jpg%2FfZy3mZ1aCwL8EYbGBDNaCqKbMQhP7TdbfHnzq3x586s%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7a6ce9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2112540/org/51454e2712824008ee5194c7ab1988ee.jpg/EVtXmbRg-xgArZXjyoITh2JPIIuVnY-cv2oodb9qKHU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2112540%2Forg%2F51454e2712824008ee5194c7ab1988ee.jpg%2FEVtXmbRg-xgArZXjyoITh2JPIIuVnY-cv2oodb9qKHU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d487327c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有傳Leonard Maltin無法看完《Suicide Mouse》，命令工作人員看完後再交筆記，豈料對方似中邪般開槍自殺。（Getty Images）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/260954/%E7%B1%B3%E5%A5%87%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A090%E6%AD%B2-%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3%E7%B1%B3%E5%A5%87%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%9D%87%E5%AE%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F260954%2F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%25BC%25A090%25E6%25AD%25B2-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%25A5%2587%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2595%25AB-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259D%2587%25E5%25AE%258C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA&d=pYblX2s1qceYPLHhGbA02p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6ee73d30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/260954/%E7%B1%B3%E5%A5%87%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A090%E6%AD%B2-%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3%E7%B1%B3%E5%A5%87%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%8B%95%E7%95%AB-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%9D%87%E5%AE%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA</a>"},{"pid":"fd8dcb325bfe3546c77c9444ea33d8069e81df05","tid":909044,"uid":107417,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"睇完表示浪費時間"},{"pid":"d190f68d0a4b89ba6be54d6ba450e9f3ff79567b","tid":909044,"uid":60303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0a211e871023e2f02feeac256a6c5e680bf2edb3","tid":909044,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}